RobotType Example

VB Example:

Select Case m_spel.RobotType

  Case SpelRobotType.Scara

    lblRobotType = "Scara"

  Case SpelRobotType.Cartesian

    lblRobotType = "Cartesian"

End Select

C# Example:

switch (m_spel.RobotType)

{
 case SpelRobotType.Scara:

   lblRobotType.Text = "Scara";

   break;
 case SpelRobotType.Cartesian:

   lblRobotType.Text = "Cartesian";

   break;
 default:

   break;

}

